      • info

        public final void info(org.spout.api.command.CommandSource source,
        org.spout.api.command.CommandArguments args)
                throws org.spout.api.exception.CommandException
        List various information about a Region. Usage is "/region info regionname"
        Parameters:
        source - The source of the command, should be a player.
        args - CommandArguements Object containing a list of all commands.
        Throws:
        org.spout.api.exception.CommandException - Thrown should anything go wrong with this command.

      • pos

        public final void pos(org.spout.api.command.CommandSource source,
       org.spout.api.command.CommandArguments args)
               throws org.spout.api.exception.CommandException
        Attempt to set a POINT for a region. Usage is "/region one" where one is the name of a point.
        Parameters:
        source - The source of the command, should be a player.
        args - CommandArguements Object containing a list of all commands.
        Throws:
        org.spout.api.exception.CommandException - Thrown should anything go wrong with this command.

      • updateregion

        public final void updateregion(org.spout.api.command.CommandSource source,
                org.spout.api.command.CommandArguments args)
                        throws org.spout.api.exception.CommandException
        Update a region that is currently held within a Player Selection. If not region, or a new region is in the selection, this will fail and direct the player what needs to be done. Usage is "/region update"
        Parameters:
        source - The source of the command, should be a player.
        args - CommandArguements Object containing a list of all commands.
        Throws:
        org.spout.api.exception.CommandException - Thrown should anything go wrong with this command.
